### Register a new user

POST http://localhost:3010/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice"
}

### Send a transaction

POST http://localhost:3010/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from_address": "0xc92e12f3a0df04e081cd2c6410c8e554b695b0dd",
  "to_address": "0xc1d158bfd476156099bfc1b701fb021d543fdb82",
  "amount": 5,
  "private_key": "d1fc08820e7cb02c289acbc99d92a11a79a649b1a941a590b1de6ee5a3f54712"
}

