### Get transaction by ID
GET http://localhost:3010/transaction/122

### get balance by address
GET http://localhost:3010/balance/0xc1d158bfd476156099bfc1b701fb021d543fdb82

### generate blocks
POST http://localhost:3010/generate-block

### get blocks
GET http://localhost:3010/blocks?limit=10&offset=0

### get detail blocks
GET http://localhost:3010/blocks/detail/2

### get block by ID
GET http://localhost:3010/blocks/2

### check blockchain integrity
GET http://localhost:3010/blocks/integrity

### get reward info
GET http://localhost:3010/reward/info

### get block reward
GET http://localhost:3010/reward/block/2

### get schedule
GET http://localhost:3010/reward/schedule/10

### get wallet balance
GET http://localhost:3010/wallet/0xc92e12f3a0df04e081cd2c6410c8e554b695b0dd?page=1&limit=5&type=received&status=confirmed&order=desc

### challenge request
POST http://localhost:3010/challenge/0xce4b0c6afb4a5c27922557f5cb3d3e1b6ef496b0

### challenge verify request
POST http://localhost:3010/challenge/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "0xce4b0c6afb4a5c27922557f5cb3d3e1b6ef496b0",
  "signature": "0x2c6404e5f3cf3f2a4d5f7c6b4c8e2f3a4b5c6d7e8f9a0b1c2d3e4f506172839405060708090a0b0c0d0e0f101112131415161718191a1b1c1d1e1f20"
}

### get market engine state
GET http://localhost:3010/market

### top-up USD balance
POST http://localhost:3010/balance/topup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "0xc09c572714aecd616928617299a338d61707448a",
  "amount": 1000,
  "reference_id": "topup-001",
  "description": "Initial top-up"
}

### get tx by block number
GET http://localhost:3010/blocks/transaction/2

### search blocks by hash
GET http://localhost:3010/blocks/search?hash=0745ddd2f15b2b3598b02a2e477ffbb5f85e3f022d26515f5cd4c8d0f1d596cf

### get blocks in range
GET http://localhost:3010/blocks/range?from=1&to=10

### get block stats
GET http://localhost:3010/blocks/stats

### search blocks by miner address
GET http://localhost:3010/blocks/search/miner?address=MINER_ACCOUNT&limit=10&offset=0

